cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

This paper focuses on image analysis and text understanding using deep learning techniques, specifically Convolutional Neural Networks (ConvNets), to recognize Arabic characters from scene images. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with natural language processing, which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with recognizing text from images. The use of deep learning techniques also falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
